nodes.text: You are trying to start a flame war?I'm not interested in statements like 'The current debacle of 'physician-assisted' suicide' because they say nothing as to what you think the debacle is or why you think it is a debacle. Likewise comments like 'any way you spin it, it's still good old-fashioned murder! Pure and simple!' just annoy because that notion has been refuted by myself and other posters on numerous occasions.
